original: Can not start network configuration utility.

No connection detected.
Check your cable connection and try again!
translation:
Nėra ryšio.
Patikrinkite, ar įjungtas tinklo kabelis, ir bandykite dar kartą!

original:
No wireless connection detected.
Double-click to start the wireless configuration wizard.
translation:
Nerastas belaidis ryšys.
Norėdami paleisti belaidžio ryšio konfigūravimo vedlį, du kartus spustelkite pele.

original: Can not open the network manager!
